(39, 78, 1, '', '2017-05-12 08:09:38', 856, 5883, 'cb83cfd0150082e76ab244544f47c4049ab68751', '{"id":78,"asset_id":249,"title":"O n\\u00e1s","alias":"o-nas","introtext":"V\\u00e1\\u0161 stabiln\\u00ed partner\\r\\nSpole\\u010dnost MULTISON s.r.o. byla zalo\\u017eena ji\\u017e v roce 1992 Eduardem Le\\u0161ingrem jako zna\\u010dkov\\u00e1 maloobchodn\\u00ed a velkoobchodn\\u00ed prodejna Goldstar s vlastn\\u00edm servisem v Hradci Kr\\u00e1lov\\u00e9. V roce 1997 do\\u0161lo k celosv\\u011btov\\u00e9 zm\\u011bn\\u011b n\\u00e1zvu zna\\u010dky Goldstar na LG ve snaze veden\\u00ed zna\\u010dky sjednotit ozna\\u010den\\u00ed v\\u00fdrobk\\u016f s n\\u00e1zvem mate\\u0159sk\\u00e9 spole\\u010dnosti LG Electronics. V roce 2002 byla podeps\\u00e1na smlouva se spole\\u010dnost\\u00ed LG Electronics, dle kter\\u00e9 se spole\\u010dnost MULTISON s.r.o. stala nositelem z\\u00e1ru\\u010dn\\u00edho servisu pro \\u010ceskou republiku. Multison postupn\\u011b vytvo\\u0159il a \\u0159\\u00eddil celorepublikovou s\\u00ed\\u0165 z\\u00e1ru\\u010dn\\u00edch certifikovan\\u00fdch servis\\u016f t\\u00e9to zna\\u010dky. Postupn\\u011b byl spole\\u010dnost\\u00ed MULTISON s.r.o. vytvo\\u0159en nejv\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed sklad origin\\u00e1ln\\u00edch n\\u00e1hradn\\u00edch d\\u00edl\\u016f v \\u010cR, byly zpracov\\u00e1ny servisn\\u00ed a u\\u017eivatelsk\\u00e9 manu\\u00e1ly ke v\\u0161em v\\u00fdrobk\\u016fm dov\\u00e1\\u017een\\u00fdm na n\\u00e1\\u0161 trh a prov\\u00e1d\\u011bno \\u0161kolen\\u00ed v\\u0161ech technik\\u016f p\\u016fsob\\u00edc\\u00edch po cel\\u00e9 republice. Na z\\u00e1klad\\u011b t\\u011bchto zku\\u0161enost\\u00ed a z\\u00e1sob\\u00e1m origin\\u00e1ln\\u00edch n\\u00e1hradn\\u00edch d\\u00edl\\u016f je i dnes prov\\u00e1d\\u011bn poz\\u00e1ru\\u010dn\\u00ed servis zn. LG, nebo\\u0165 od r. 2008 zna\\u010dka LG p\\u0159e\\u0161la na jin\\u00fd syst\\u00e9m servisn\\u00edho zaji\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed v \\u010cR a MULTISON s.r.o. se st\\u00e1v\\u00e1 odpov\\u011bdn\\u00fdm servisn\\u00edm centrem pro oblast v\\u00fdchodn\\u00ed \\u010cechy (elektronika) a servis b\\u00edl\\u00e9 techniky v\\u0161ech zna\\u010dek prod\\u00e1van\\u00fdch v \\u010cR.\\r\\nJsme obchodn\\u00edm zastoupen\\u00edm spole\\u010dnosti NFL pro \\u010ceskou a Slovenskou republiku.\\r\\nOd roku 2011 se spole\\u010dnost Multison s.r.o. zam\\u011b\\u0159ila na nov\\u00e9 perspektivn\\u00ed technologie, zejm\\u00e9na na vysoce \\u00fasporn\\u00e9 LED technologie t\\u00fdkaj\\u00edc\\u00ed se vnit\\u0159n\\u00edho a venkovn\\u00edho osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed. V sou\\u010dasn\\u00e9 dob\\u011b je MULTISON s.r.o. obchodn\\u00ed z\\u00e1stupce pro \\u010cR a v\\u00fdhradn\\u00ed z\\u00e1stupce pro SR spole\\u010dnosti NFL (RU). Jedn\\u00e1 se o v\\u011bdecko-v\\u00fdzkumn\\u00fd a v\\u00fdrobn\\u00ed podnik zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00fd na letectv\\u00ed a kosmonautiku s dlouholet\\u00fdmi zku\\u0161enostmi v oblasti v\\u00fdvoje a v\\u00fdroby osv\\u011btlovac\\u00edch syst\\u00e9m\\u016f. se s\\u00eddlem ve Voron\\u011b\\u017ei (RU). Tento v\\u00fdrobn\\u00ed komplex ve sv\\u00fdch v\\u00fdrobc\\u00edch vyu\\u017e\\u00edv\\u00e1 Sv\\u00edtidla t\\u00e9to spole\\u010dnosti jsou osazov\\u00e1na LED \\u010dipy od americk\\u00e9 spole\\u010dnosti CREE, co\\u017e zaru\\u010duje nejvy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed kvalitu sv\\u00edtidel. v\\u00fdrobk\\u016f jak ve\\u0159ejn\\u00e9ho, tak i pr\\u016fmyslov\\u00e9ho osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed. Tyto v\\u00fdrobky jsou ji\\u017e realizov\\u00e1ny T\\u011bmito sv\\u00edtidly jsou ji\\u017e osazeny nap\\u0159. POLYGON v Hradci Kr\\u00e1lov\\u00e9, ve\\u0159ejn\\u00e9 osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed od vlakov\\u00e9ho n\\u00e1dra\\u017e\\u00ed kolem TESCA v Hradci Kr\\u00e1lov\\u00e9, obce Veliny, Os\\u00edk, \\u010castolovice a dal\\u0161\\u00ed, komplexn\\u00ed osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed pr\\u016fmyslov\\u00fdch v\\u00fdrobn\\u00edch hal ve Zl\\u00edn\\u011b atd. \\/viz. reference\\/ V sou\\u010dasn\\u00e9 dob\\u011b krom\\u011b aktivn\\u00ed obchodn\\u00ed \\u010dinnosti v oblasti LED osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed firma MULTISON s.r.o. prov\\u00e1d\\u00ed poz\\u00e1ru\\u010dn\\u00ed servis v\\u00fdrobk\\u016f v\\u0161ech zna\\u010dek spot\\u0159ebn\\u00ed elektroniky a b\\u00edl\\u00e9 techniky.televizor\\u016f, videop\\u0159ehr\\u00e1va\\u010d\\u016f, DVD, zesilova\\u010d\\u016f, mix\\u00e1\\u017en\\u00edch pult\\u016f, pra\\u010dek a my\\u010dek.","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"19","created":"2017-05-12 08:09:38","created_by":"856","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2017-05-12 08:09:38","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2017-05-12 08:09:38","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_page_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\"