 n\\u00e1hradn\\u00edch d\\u00edl\\u016f je i dnes prov\\u00e1d\\u011bn poz\\u00e1ru\\u010dn\\u00ed servis zn. <strong>LG<\\/strong>, nebo\\u0165 od r. 2008 zna\\u010dka <strong>LG<\\/strong> p\\u0159e\\u0161la na jin\\u00fd syst\\u00e9m servisn\\u00edho zaji\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed v \\u010cR a <strong>MULTISON s.r.o.<\\/strong> se st\\u00e1v\\u00e1 odpov\\u011bdn\\u00fdm servisn\\u00edm centrem pro oblast v\\u00fdchodn\\u00ed \\u010cechy (elektronika) a servis b\\u00edl\\u00e9 techniky v\\u0161ech zna\\u010dek prod\\u00e1van\\u00fdch v \\u010cR.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><strong>Jsme obchodn\\u00edm zastoupen\\u00edm spole\\u010dnosti NFL pro \\u010ceskou a Slovenskou republiku.<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Od roku 2011 se spole\\u010dnost <strong>Multison s.r.o.<\\/strong> zam\\u011b\\u0159ila na nov\\u00e9 perspektivn\\u00ed technologie, zejm\\u00e9na na vysoce \\u00fasporn\\u00e9 <strong>LED<\\/strong> technologie t\\u00fdkaj\\u00edc\\u00ed se vnit\\u0159n\\u00edho a venkovn\\u00edho osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed. V sou\\u010dasn\\u00e9 dob\\u011b je <strong>MULTISON s.r.o.<\\/strong> obchodn\\u00ed z\\u00e1stupce pro \\u010cR a v\\u00fdhradn\\u00ed z\\u00e1stupce pro SR spole\\u010dnosti <strong>NFL<\\/strong> (RU). Jedn\\u00e1 se o v\\u011bdecko-v\\u00fdzkumn\\u00fd a v\\u00fdrobn\\u00ed podnik zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00fd na letectv\\u00ed a kosmonautiku s dlouholet\\u00fdmi zku\\u0161enostmi v oblasti v\\u00fdvoje a v\\u00fdroby osv\\u011btlovac\\u00edch syst\\u00e9m\\u016f. se s\\u00eddlem ve Voron\\u011b\\u017ei (RU). Tento v\\u00fdrobn\\u00ed komplex ve sv\\u00fdch v\\u00fdrobc\\u00edch vyu\\u017e\\u00edv\\u00e1 Sv\\u00edtidla t\\u00e9to spole\\u010dnosti jsou osazov\\u00e1na LED \\u010dipy od americk\\u00e9 spole\\u010dnosti <strong>CREE<\\/strong>, co\\u017e zaru\\u010duje nejvy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed kvalitu sv\\u00edtidel. v\\u00fdrobk\\u016f jak ve\\u0159ejn\\u00e9ho, tak i pr\\u016fmyslov\\u00e9ho osv\\u011btlen\\u00ed. Tyto v\\u00fdrobky jsou ji\\u017e realizov\\u0